<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/788986-for-what-ages-could-this-book-be">for what ages could this book be?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_788986'><a id="like_count_community_question_788986" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/788986?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">11 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F25541028-elon-musk">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/788986-for-what-ages-could-this-book-be">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/788986-for-what-ages-could-this-book-be">See all 5 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/12935853-julie-hendrix"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1347975630i/12935853._UX100_CR0,5,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/12935853-julie-hendrix">Julie Hendrix</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">if a young person is curious and motivated to learn about space rockets, electric cars, and some related history, then i think someone as young as 11-<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">if a young person is curious and motivated to learn about space rockets, electric cars, and some related history, then i think someone as young as 11-12 might read all or part(s) of this book. the author goes into great detail, but the entire biographical story is compelling. there is also a lot of info about the early days of the internet, musk's ancestors and immediate family, and historical info on paypal and solar city. musk is a fascinating person, and i believe his story has a wide appeal.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
